# Escena 3D con @{three}
> Three.js interactivo - arrastra para rotar

@{three}
background #f0f4f8
gridhelper size:10 divisions:10
axes
box 0 0.5 0 size:1,1,1 color:#2196f3
sphere 2 1 0 r:0.5 color:#f44336
cylinder -2 0.75 0 r:0.3 h:1.5 color:#4caf50
cone 0 1 2 r:0.5 h:1 color:#ff9800
arrow 0 0 0 0 3 0 color:#00ff00
arrow 0 0 0 3 0 0 color:#ff0000
arrow 0 0 0 0 0 3 color:#0000ff
camera 4 4 4 lookat:0,1,0
@{end three}

## Datos
L = 5
H = 3
Vol = L * L * H